channel.desc: Comedy 2006 Garfield and Prince are two typical-looking cats. Surprisingly, Lady Elanor leaves Carlyle Castle to Prince, which enrages her nephew, the Lord Dargis, who wants to get rid of Prince. Breckin Meyer, Jennifer Love Hewitt, Billy Connolly, Bill Murray, Roger Rees, Tim Hill, Steven Rimdzius, Joel Cohen, Alec Sokolow.
